headline: Morgan Stanley cuts ADM, Bunge targets on weaker 2025 outlook
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley lowered its price targets on Archer-Daniels-Midland Company (NYSE:ADM) and Bunge Limited (NYSE:BG)due to a weaker-than-expected 2025 outlook and earnings pressure.
